{"tid":1058044,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[FIBA] 2019年籃球世界盃 將於3月16日舉行分組抽籤","createTime":"2019-03-12T09:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T09:43:32.000Z","uid":18692,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"977dbe76132a26822c5c9bfa9ca2c39a7dcea2e3","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VK4jLjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVK4jLjt.jpg&h=10b6aa42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本屆籃球世界盃由8個城市舉辦，而廣東就佔了4個。賽事於8月31日開幕，決賽為9月15日。參賽國家由24個增加至32個，將分為8組、一組4個國家。 <br />\n<br />\n每組前兩名晉級下一輪比賽。16隊按照小組賽成績分成4組，前兩名晉級8強並以淘汰賽方式產生冠軍。 <br />\n<br />\n今個星期六(16/3)香港時間晚上6時半將會由高比拜仁及姚明領銜，進行分組抽籤。前兩次亞洲國家主辦為1978年菲律賓及2006年日本的世界錦標賽。<br />\n<br />\n香港於亞太區外圍賽首輪出局，同組有紐西蘭、南韓及中國。"},{"pid":"eec99e0e272cd14eee8e0c47ece51a98b34a1371","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:28:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EbeMFW9rIA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEbeMFW9rIA4&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LawKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=92a5f4cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EbeMFW9rIA4</a><br />\n16/3 (六) 18:30開始<br />\n直播抽籤"},{"pid":"819d48c181388946f1499bed28f672b2a844d1d8","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:29:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一檔（世界排名）<br />\n美國 (1)、西班牙 (2)、法國 (3)、塞爾維亞 (4)、阿根廷 (5)、立陶宛 (6)、希臘 (8)、中國 (30)<br />\n<br />\n其他晉級球隊<br />\n歐洲：俄羅斯 (10)、意大利 (13)、土耳其 (17)、德國 (22)、捷克 (24)、 波蘭 (25)、黑山 (28)<br />\n美洲：巴西 (12) 、波多黎各 (16)、多明尼加 (18)、委內瑞拉 (20) 、加拿大 (23)  <br />\n亞太區：澳洲 (11)、伊朗 (27)、菲律賓 (31)、南韓 (32)、紐西蘭 (38)、日本 (48)、約旦 (49) <br />\n非洲：尼日利亞 (33)、塞內加爾 (37)、安哥拉 (39)、突尼西亞 (51)、科特迪瓦 (64)</span>"},{"pid":"fa60cd37d70d142dc9fee6fa46da82cf099d3c40","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:31:21.000Z","msg":"主辦城市<br />\n分組賽（一, 二輪）<br />\n上海、深圳、南京、廣州、佛山、北京、東莞、武漢<br />\n<br />\n8強及5-8名排位賽<br />\n上海（6場） <br />\n東莞（6場）<br />\n<br />\n4強, 第5,7名, 季軍戰及決賽（6場）<br />\n北京"},{"pid":"41341b0ea6434668fb267dc7b95786757048e142","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HnZjLr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHnZjLr1.jpg&h=a4c8a8be&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n票價表"},{"pid":"bdb1ddd1381b5fbd593b98707ffc69474ec61e40","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:57:51.000Z","msg":"球隊套票（3場分組賽+2場複賽/排名賽）<br />\n4月12號截止    9折優惠<br />\n訂金：A檔 1,000 / B檔 800 / C檔 500<br />\n有All Games選項，球隊晉級8強後付款（3場）<br />\n<br />\n買飛網址<br />\n<a href=\"https://WorldCup.Basketball/Tickets\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2FWorldCup.Basketball%2FTickets&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0LawKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=d9b5f1fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://WorldCup.Basketball/Tickets</a>"},{"pid":"29ba00b96d9ca80de7a64904d73c8a2af94d581f","tid":1058044,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T12:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8b2f17b90bff3ea2463e71e20aa3c63d694f7aed","tid":1058044,"uid":236691,"like":15,"dislike":12,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T13:35:21.000Z","msg":"籃球學人搞世界盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596600ddf9903ee29b39ef01fde5a38a8bbcf890","tid":1058044,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T15:44:31.000Z","msg":"城市套票會喺抽籤之後賣<br />\n有A至D檔"},{"pid":"dd2a456c227c8a43b2a478759ddeec8547033ac4","tid":1058044,"uid":164476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8b2f17b90bff3ea2463e71e20aa3c63d694f7aed","tid":1058044,"uid":236691,"like":15,"dislike":12,"score":3,"citedBy":2,